    * **Sub-structure 2 (Taller):** This is a three-layered structure. The bottom layer consists of a green block (index 10) in a vertical orientation. The middle layer is a yellow block (index 11) placed on top of the green block.  The top layer contains a red arched block (index 2) on which a  orange triangular block (index 15) sits.

**3. Determine the Assembly Order:**

The assembly order needs to consider building the two sub-structures separately and then placing them next to each other.  This description prioritizes a bottom-up approach.
